# Docker Secrets Directory
# All files in this directory are gitignored for security
#
# Required files for production deployment:
#
# 1. database_password
#    Database password (PostgreSQL, MySQL, etc.)
#
# 2. redis_password
#    Redis authentication password
#
# 3. rails_secret_key_base
#    Rails secret key base (generate with: rails secret)
#
# 4. cf_tunnel_token (optional)
#    Cloudflare Tunnel token for remote access
#
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Copy example files and remove .example suffix
# 2. Generate secure passwords (use: openssl rand -base64 32)
# 3. Never commit these files to git!
